Now that we have <math>M\mathrm{T}C</math> and <math>\mathrm{T}C</math>, we can plug them into our formula for <math>G</math>:


<math>
\scriptsize
𝒈 = 
\begin{array} {ccc}
𝒋 \\
\left[ \begin{matrix}
1200.000 & 1901.955 & 2786.314 \\
