Then all that's left to do is multiply everything through. 


<math>
𝒈 = 
\begin{array} {ccc}
𝒋\mathrm{T}C\left(M\mathrm{T}C)^\mathsf{T}(M\mathrm{T}C(M\mathrm{T}C)^\mathsf{T}\right)^{-1} \\
